name: Phase Lab Experimental Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the experimental ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the Phase Lab. Contains some secret experimental platforms not in the codex yet.

name: Phase Lab Navy Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the navy-standard ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the Phase Lab

name: Phase Lab Commercial Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the market-available ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the Phase Lab

name: Phase Lab Domain Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct the domain era ship hulls, weapons, and fighter LPCs from the Phase Lab

name: Principles of Phase Resonance
desc: An electronic version of the tedious instructions about how to use phase resonance to disrupt electronic systems. It tells you how to make military usage of the phase resonance phenomenon.
